il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser.general

Class CachedFunction<T,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • il.ac.technion.nlp.nli.parser.general.CachedFunction<T,R>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Function<T,R>

    public class CachedFunction<T,R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.function.Function<T,R>
    Just like Function, but calculates the function only the first time apply(Object) is called per arguments (in following calls - the previously calculated value is returned). Memory note: CachedFunction holds all objects it ever created (i.e. the result of the function application).
